oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Paving North 5th Street, c.1960s
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of North 5th Street being paved for the Townhouse Village housing development, located in the East Nashville urban renewal area. Photographed by the Nashville Housing Authority, c. early 1960s. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
